  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, single-blind, trial to determine whether a high-protein, low calorie diet is more
      effective than a control low calorie diet in improving the metabolic and histologic
      abnormalities in patients with Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease undergoing bariatric
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
